  17,1,"Kronkron Hene no ne Nea ∆Üde Na‚Äôkoa (Muhammad) tuu kwan anadwo firi (Maka) Nyamedan kronkron no ho kÕªÕª (Yerusalam) Aqsoa Nyamedan a nhyira atwa ho ahyia no ho no, sŒµdeŒµ YŒµ‚ÄôbŒµkyerŒµ no YŒµn nsŒµnkyerŒµnee no mu bi. NokorŒµ sŒµ ∆Üne OtiefoÕª no a ∆Üte biribiara na ∆Üno ara nso na Ohunu biribiara"
