  24,3,"AdwamammÕªni barima nni ho kwan s‘ë ·¥êware‘ë, gyes‘ë adwamammÕªni baa, anaasŒµ Õªbosomsomni baa; adwamammÕªni baa nso nni ho kwan s‘ë y‘ëware no, gyes‘ë adwamammÕªni barima anaasŒµ Õªbosomsomni barima; yabra agyidiefoÕª saa (awadeŒµ no)"
